# plaid-backgrounds
Get background colors for Plaid images

**Example 1**
```
const allyLogo = "";
getBackgroundColor(logo).then(color => {
  console.log(color); // #602962
);
```

**Example 2**
```
const amexLogo = "";
getBackgroundColor(logo).then(color => {
  console.log(color); // #F4F5F7
);
```
